description: Returns the bundles that can be applied to your Amazon Lightsail content delivery network (CDN) distributions. A distribution bundle specifies the monthly network transfer quota and monthly cost of your distribution.

nested_items.name: bundles
nested_items.description: An object that describes a distribution bundle.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the distribution bundle.

nested_items.name: price
nested_items.description: The monthly price, in US dollars, of the bundle.

nested_items.name: transferPerMonthInGb
nested_items.description: The monthly network transfer quota of the bundle.

nested_items.name: isActive
nested_items.description: Indicates whether the bundle is active, and can be specified for a new or existing distribution.
